    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Let An-gels’ ho-ly choirs be a-mazed at the won-der; and let us mor-tals cry out a hymn__ with our voic-es, be-hold-ing God’s mar-vel-lous con-de-scen--sion tran-scend-ing speech: He at Whom the pow-ers of the Heav-ens do trem-ble, Him do a-ged arms take in their ten-der em-brace now, the on-ly true Friend__ of__ man. \n\nthe on-ly true Friend__ of__ man.____"
    }
